{
  "stem": "14156.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They-- they did everything they could, I assume.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But they-- after about three weeks, three, four weeks, she passed away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I-- it was on a Sabbath, on a Shabbos.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I, I was in bed and I heard downstairs crying and, and, and screaming.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know what people do after they find somebody is dead?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They, they-- you know, they, they disbelief and everything like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All of a sudden, my father comes up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he, he tells me, you know, your mother passed away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She's [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I hugged him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, OK, Papa.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I still have you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So from there on, the funeral wasn't-- it was in another couple days.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so we buried Mom.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that ended the, this episode.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I, I can remember weeks later, Father was always, you know straight out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he-- I guess it come from World War I when he was in the war.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we were bicycling-- he with his and mine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We go to the temple to [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH], to the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So he said, you know, now your mother is nothing like-- left but just a skeleton.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He looked at me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He said, yes, well, that's the nature of things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That's the way it happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And I, well, I had to cope with it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But he, you know, he, he, he let me know that that's the way we all will end up.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, after one year, we-- OK, we had to sit shiva, if you know what that is.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was for me the first time-- no shoes, only socks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you had to sit lower than chairs, regular chairs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And every night, people used to come.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
